# APISignalProbe - HTTP Endpoint Monitor

APISignalProbe performs fast checks on a batch of APIs to track responsiveness and uptime issues.

## Features
- Multi-endpoint scan  
- Console and file logging  
- Adjustable timeout  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_APISignalProbe.git
cd 24_APISignalProbe
python monitor.py
